# PURPOSE:
# Provides in-dashboard documentation for a feature.
# Helps users understand what a feature does, how it works,
# and what settings control its behavior.
#
# PLACEMENT:
# - First card in the Automations tab
# - Can also appear in Overview tab if needed
#
# PLACEHOLDERS:
#   {feature}           - Feature name (e.g., "hvac", "security")
#   {feature_title}     - Human-readable title (e.g., "HVAC Control")
#   {goal_description}  - What this feature achieves
#   {method_description}- How it achieves the goal
#   {date}              - Last update date
#
# USAGE:
# 1. Copy to your dashboard
# 2. Replace all placeholders
# 3. Fill in the specific details for your feature
# 4. Keep updated when feature behavior changes

