# =============================================================================
# TIPS FOR WRITING GOOD DOCUMENTATION
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. GOAL SECTION
#    - State the user benefit, not technical details
#    - Good: "Automatically locks doors when everyone leaves home"
#    - Bad: "Uses person entities to trigger lock service"
#
# 2. METHOD SECTION
#    - Explain the logic flow in plain language
#    - Include key thresholds and timings
#    - Mention any user-visible behaviors
#
# 3. TRIGGERS TABLE
#    - List ALL triggers that can cause this feature to act
#    - Include both automatic and manual triggers
#    - Note any conditions that must be met
#
# 4. SETTINGS DEPENDENCIES
#    - Show live values using {{ states() }} templates
#    - Link to Settings tab where values can be changed
#    - Explain what happens at different values
#
# 5. KEEP IT UPDATED
#    - Update when behavior changes
#    - Update when settings are added/removed
#    - Include last-updated date for reference
#
# =============================================================================
